### 1. Get All Courses
GET http://localhost:8085/api/courses
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Add a New Course
POST http://localhost:8085/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "101",
  "name": "Spring Boot Basics",
  "description": "Introductory course to Spring Boot"
}

###

### 3. Get Course by ID
GET http://localhost:8085/api/courses/101
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Update Existing Course
PUT http://localhost:8085/api/courses/101
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "101",
  "name": "Spring Boot Updated",
  "description": "Updated course on Spring Boot"
}

###

### 5. Delete Course by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8085/api/courses/101

###

### 6. Search Course by Name
GET http://localhost:8085/api/courses/search?name=Spring
Accept: application/json